By addressing privacy, security and ownership concerns of DNA testing and sharing, we are building the worldâ€™s largest user-owned genomic data bank to secure the future of personalised medicine. $GNOME is the GenomesDAO governance token. Holders can influence decisions concerning the project such as proposing or deciding on new feature proposals and even changing the governance system itself.
